rComments: Very boring TA. She assigns readings then goes over them during the following class period the whole time. Super boring and asked extremely specific questions. Even when I did the readings I didn't know the answers. Wish I didn't take her class. Got absolutely nothing out of it. If you miss more than 2 classes your grade gets docked by 3%...
Didn't really enjoy her teaching style and didn't feel she was well qualified to teach the class.
